{"title":"Geriatrica","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología/ORL Geriatrica iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"ORL GERIÁTRICA\\N→ Lo que el\\NGeriatra debe saber","guid":"Kh5cSrxzPiOyIn3dbWUa1w","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"HIPOACUSIA EN\\NPERSONA MAYOR","guid":"wwqjiBV8xdQWBNO67CKjsg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Presbiacusia → causa MÁS frecuente de sordera en AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Prevalencia >65a → 52% autopercepción (ENS Chile 2009-2010)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"Prevalencia >75a → >70% algún grado de hipoacusia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"2","text":"FACTOR DE RIESGO MODIFICABLE para demencia → Lancet Commission 2020","guid":"","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"Mayor contribuyente individual → 8.2% del riesgo atribuible poblacional","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"2","text":"Hipoacusia NO tratada → depresión, aislamiento, deterioro cognitivo, caídas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"Fisiopatología\\Npresbiacusia","guid":"4j9_AJt7dSU5IX-xwHe68g","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Neurosensorial bilateral simétrica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"Degeneración coclear → células ciliadas externas (base coclear primero)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"Patrón audiométrico → caída en frecuencias agudas (2000-8000 Hz)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"9","text":"Componente neural → degeneración del nervio auditivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"9","text":"Componente central → procesamiento auditivo alterado → oye pero no entiende","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"9","text":"Factores agravantes → ruido acumulativo, ototóxicos, DM, dislipidemia, tabaco","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"1","text":"Tamizaje y\\Ndiagnóstico","guid":"p5ziGskFfqhb4w6d2VZDig","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"EMPAM → pregunta simple: tiene dificultad para escuchar?","guid":"","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"Autorreporte sensibilidad 71-93% para hipoacusia >=40 dB","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"Otoscopía → SIEMPRE → descartar tapón cerumen (30% de AM con hipoacusia)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"Extracción cerumen = intervención COSTO-EFECTIVA en geriatría","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"16","text":"Audiometría tonal → GOLD STANDARD","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"PTP = promedio 500, 1000, 2000, 4000 Hz","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"16","text":"Clasificación OMS\\Nsegún PTP mejor oído","guid":"ndtOI_J8HKKpKBYbvWmG7A","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"Normal: <=25 dB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"Leve: 26-40 dB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"Moderada: 41-60 dB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"23","text":"Severa: 61-80 dB","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"23","text":"Profunda: >80 dB","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"16","text":"Logoaudiometría → discriminación de palabra","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"Clave para predecir beneficio de audífono vs implante coclear","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"16","text":"Impedanciometría → función oído medio","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"1","text":"AUDÍFONO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Indicación\\NGES Chile","guid":"lbYeexjGG6Xi6rXvwcqLMQ","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"PTP >=40 dB mejor oído → indicación absoluta (audífono uniaural)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"PTP 35-40 dB + HHIE-S >=10 → indicación relativa","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"32","text":"Tipos\\Nprincipales","guid":"Td34WQPVEJmLyAWkChO_rQ","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Retroauricular (BTE) → más usado en AM, fácil manipulación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Intracanal (ITC/CIC) → estética, menor potencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"Digital con múltiples micrófonos → mayor satisfacción","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"32","text":"Factores para\\Néxito en AM","guid":"_J5P75DPkXx3Wsann5bmkg","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Motivación del paciente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"Destreza manual → manipulación dispositivo y pilas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"Estado cognitivo → capacidad de aprendizaje","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"40","text":"Red de apoyo → familia involucrada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"40","text":"Expectativas realistas → mejora comunicación, NO restaura audición normal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"32","text":"Adherencia →\\NPROBLEMA MAYOR","guid":"vhXYgXEmmOdrUdIshy4nIg","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"Solo 40-50% uso correcto en estudios nacionales chilenos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"Causas de abandono → incomodidad, ruido ambiental, estigma, deterioro cognitivo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"32","text":"Seguimiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"Fonoaudiólogo/TMed → anual","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"ORL + audiometría → cada 5 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"Segundo audífono → tras 1 año de buena adherencia","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"1","text":"IMPLANTE\\NCOCLEAR","guid":"eiNfesPvE_7p3GBJ2Ym6lQ","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Definición → dispositivo electrónico que estimula directamente nervio auditivo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"Indicación\\Nen AM","guid":"kGMCeV6DEH_Pd2sX94DXEQ","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"Hipoacusia severa-profunda bilateral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"Beneficio insuficiente con audífonos optimizados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"55","text":"Discriminación <50% en logoaudiometría con audífonos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"SIN límite de edad superior para candidatura","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"53","text":"Evidencia en >60 años\\N(Cuda 2024, BMC Geriatr)","guid":"se03qAqoEFrTqZVKBp03Dw","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"N=100, multinacional, edad media 71.7 años (rango 60-91)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"HUI3 mejoró +0.13 a 18 meses (p<0.001)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"Escala De Jong Loneliness redujo -0.61 (p=0.014)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"Lawton AIVD mejoró +1.25 (p<0.001)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"60","text":"HHIE-S redujo -8.7 puntos (handicap significativo a leve-moderado)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"60","text":"Beneficio INDEPENDIENTE del grupo etario (60-64, 65-74, 75+)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"60","text":"100% alcanzó discriminación sin lectura labial post-implante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"60","text":">=50% uso de teléfono con interlocutor conocido","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"69","parent":"53","text":"Evaluación\\Npre-implante\\Ngeriátrica","guid":"MeYFaGVXrbr8mWux_LCLzA","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"VGI completa → funcional, cognitivo, fragilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"TAC/RMN temporal → anatomía coclear","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"Expectativas y motivación del paciente y familia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"69","text":"Rehabilitación auditiva post-operatoria → ESENCIAL (mínimo 6-12 meses)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"53","text":"Resultado → mejora calidad de vida, independencia, menor soledad","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"0","text":"VÉRTIGO EN\\NPERSONA MAYOR","guid":"bbCqpeVoF9qSNqNqxCswbw","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Abordaje clínico →\\NPERFIL TEMPORAL es la\\Nclave","guid":"5dfr7s00eULW1_1bpy32Mw","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"Preguntas\\Nfundamentales","guid":"h_FTeupI5-pV7ArYPNddDQ","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"Cómo fue? (giro vs inestabilidad vs mareo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"Cuándo partió?","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"77","text":"Cuánto duró? (segundos, minutos, horas, días)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"77","text":"Posicional? Espontáneo?","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"77","text":"Síntomas acompañantes → audición, cefalea, neurológicos","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"75","text":"EPISÓDICOS →\\NCrisis cortas (<1 min)","guid":"9nSC2XC0vPFTlm_4pGRHBA","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"VPPB → EL MÁS FRECUENTE","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Episodios gatillados por movimientos (girarse en cama, agacharse)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"Diagnóstico → maniobra de Dix-Hallpike positiva","guid":"","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"Nistagmo torsional geotrópico, latencia, fatigable","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"84","text":"Canal posterior → 80% de los casos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"84","text":"Canal horizontal → variante, nistagmo horizontal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"84","text":"Tratamiento → maniobras de reposición (Epley, Semont)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Efectividad >80% en primera sesión","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"CONTRAINDICADO sedantes vestibulares crónicos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"84","text":"Recurrencia ~50% a 5 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"84","text":"En AM → considerar osteoporosis, déficit vitamina D como factores","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"83","text":"Ortostatismo hemodinámico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"MUY frecuente en AM → sobremedicación antihipertensiva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"Criterios Bárány Society (Kim 2019)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Mareo/vértigo al ponerse de pie","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"Hipotensión ortostática documentada (caída PAS >=20 o PAD >=10)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"Resolución al sentarse/acostarse","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"95","text":"Causas → antihipertensivos, diuréticos, falla autonómica, deshidratación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"95","text":"Manejo → revisar fármacos, medias compresivas, hidratación, fludrocortisona","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"83","text":"TIA fosa posterior → RARO pero peligroso","guid":"","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"Vértigo aislado corto + factores de riesgo vascular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"Pensar si >60a + HTA + DM + FA","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"83","text":"Paroxismia vestibular","guid":"","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"Episodios muy cortos y recurrentes (~segundos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"106","text":"Compresión neurovascular del VIII par en APC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"106","text":"Responde a carbamazepina/oxcarbazepina","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"110","parent":"75","text":"EPISÓDICOS →\\NCrisis largas\\N(minutos a horas)","guid":"6bHonhlQirJS4n2doBM3nw","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"Enfermedad de Menière","guid":"","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"Criterios Bárány (Lopez-Escamez 2015)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":">=2 episodios de vértigo espontáneo 20 min-12 hrs","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"HNS fluctuante en frecuencias bajas-medias ipsilateral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"Síntomas aurales fluctuantes (tinnitus, plenitud ótica)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"111","text":"Fisiopatología → hidrops endolinfático","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"111","text":"Manejo → dieta hiposódica, diuréticos, betahistina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"111","text":"En AM → diagnóstico diferencial con vestibulopatía bilateral","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"110","text":"Migraña vestibular","guid":"","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"Criterios Bárány-IHS (Lempert 2012)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":">=5 episodios vestibulares 5 min-72 hrs","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"Historia actual o pasada de migraña (ICHD)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"120","text":">=1 característica migrañosa en >=50% episodios","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"120","text":"No mejor explicado por otro diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"119","text":"50% episodios asociados a cefalea migrañosa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"119","text":"Prevalencia ~1% población general","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"119","text":"Manejo → profilaxis migrañosa (propranolol, amitriptilina, topiramato)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"75","text":"AGUDOS →\\NSíndrome\\Nvestibular agudo","guid":"symy9QwGWkdk-7Q3_P6cew","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"DIAGNÓSTICO DIFERENCIAL CRÍTICO → ACV vs Neuritis vestibular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"Neuritis vestibular\\N(AUVP - Strupp 2022)","guid":"xjOtyonwHRoalH_Lkuq45w","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"Vértigo agudo sostenido >24 hrs","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"130","text":"Nistagmo espontáneo horizontal-torsional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"130","text":"Test impulso cefálico (+) → sacada correctiva ipsilesional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"130","text":"SIN hipoacusia, SIN síntomas neurológicos centrales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"130","text":"Incidencia 3.5-15.5/100,000/año","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"130","text":"Manejo → corticoides fase aguda, rehabilitación vestibular precoz","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"137","parent":"128","text":"HINTS → ALGORITMO para\\Ndiferenciar central vs periférico","guid":"YgUbuvNhA10t5fYBB16e6w","children":[{"id":"138","parent":"137","text":"H → Head Impulse → Normal = PELIGROSO (central)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"137","text":"IN → Nystagmus → Dirección cambiante = CENTRAL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"137","text":"TS → Test of Skew → Positivo = CENTRAL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"137","text":"Sensibilidad >96% para ACV (> RMN en primeras 48 hrs)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"137","text":"CUALQUIER signo central → neuroimagen URGENTE","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"143","parent":"128","text":"RED FLAGS → Cuándo\\Npensar en CENTRAL","guid":"iRggyUZ4fb0v9eHq8IE5yw","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"Nistagmo vertical puro o dirección cambiante","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"Test impulso cefálico NORMAL + vértigo agudo severo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"Skew deviation","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"143","text":"Déficit neurológico focal (disartria, ataxia, diplopía)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"143","text":"Cefalea severa de inicio súbito","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"143","text":"Factores de riesgo vascular (edad, HTA, DM, FA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"143","text":"Inicio hiperagudo","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"151","parent":"75","text":"CRÓNICOS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"Vestibulopatía bilateral","guid":"","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"Asociada a edad → PRESBIVESTIBULOPATÍA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"Secundaria a ototóxicos → aminoglucósidos, diuréticos de asa, QMT","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"Idiopática","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"152","text":"Síntomas → inestabilidad crónica, oscilopsia, caídas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"152","text":"Diagnóstico → vHIT bilateral alterado, prueba calórica bilateral reducida","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"151","text":"MPPP (Mareo Postural Perceptual Persistente)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"Personalidad ansiosa + evento vestibular previo (ej: neuritis)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"Mala compensación central","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"158","text":"Inestabilidad al estar de pie, mejora en reposo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"158","text":"Se suma a sarcopenia, problemas articulares","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"158","text":"Manejo → rehabilitación kinesiológica + ISRS","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"164","parent":"75","text":"Evaluación complementaria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"Síntomas acompañantes → hipoacusia/tinnitus, cefalea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"Gatillantes → posición (VPPB), ruido/Valsalva (3ra ventana)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"164","text":"Síndrome de 3ra ventana","guid":"","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"Oído normal → 2 ventanas (oval + redonda)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"3ra ventana → energía no se disipa → vértigo + hipoacusia por ruido/Valsalva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"167","text":"Causas → dehiscencia canal semicircular superior (más frecuente hoy)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"167","text":"Otras → sífilis terciaria (goma), OMC colesteatomatosa","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"172","parent":"0","text":"REHABILITACIÓN SENSORIAL\\NEN PERSONA MAYOR","guid":"16FjpmXj5hTTRkOEx7SAsQ","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"Concepto → intervención ESENCIAL, no opcional","guid":"","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"Deprivación sensorial → factor precipitante de delirium, deterioro funcional, caídas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"Corrección sensorial → estrategia de PREVENCIÓN primaria en geriatría","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"172","text":"Rehabilitación auditiva","guid":"","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"Adaptación de audífono → proceso (NO acto único)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"178","parent":"177","text":"Educación paciente + familia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"177","text":"Estrategias comunicativas ACE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"177","text":"Rehabilitación grupal → eficaz (reduce estigma, aislamiento)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"177","text":"Ajuste progresivo del dispositivo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"176","text":"Post implante coclear → mínimo 6-12 meses de terapia fonoaudiológica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"176","text":"Impacto funcional geriátrico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"Mejora interacción social → reduce aislamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"183","text":"Mejora función cognitiva → Lancet Commission evidencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"183","text":"Mejora AIVD → Lawton (Cuda 2024, mejoría +1.25 puntos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"183","text":"Reduce riesgo de caídas (componente auditivo del equilibrio)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"188","parent":"172","text":"Rehabilitación vestibular","guid":"","children":[{"id":"189","parent":"188","text":"Indicaciones → TODA vestibulopatía periférica (aguda, crónica, bilateral)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"188","text":"Principio → compensación central mediante neuroplasticidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"188","text":"Componentes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"Ejercicios de habituación → exposición progresiva a movimientos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"Ejercicios de estabilización de mirada (VOR) → gaze stabilization","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"191","text":"Entrenamiento de equilibrio estático y dinámico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"191","text":"Entrenamiento de doble tarea → dual-task training","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"188","text":"En AM → adaptación a comorbilidades","guid":"","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"Sarcopenia → fortalecer base muscular previamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"Déficit visual → compensar input visual","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"196","text":"Polifarmacia → reducir sedantes vestibulares","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"196","text":"Miedo a caer → abordaje psicológico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"188","text":"Evidencia → mejora balance, marcha, reduce riesgo caídas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"188","text":"Tecnología emergente → posturografía móvil, wearable sensors","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"203","parent":"172","text":"MENSAJE CLAVE para el geriatra","guid":"","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"PREGUNTAR activamente por hipoacusia y mareo/vértigo en TODA VGI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"203","text":"DERIVAR oportunamente → ORL para audiometría y evaluación vestibular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"203","text":"NO normalizar → la pérdida sensorial tiene consecuencias graves y TRATABLES","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"203","text":"REHABILITAR → como parte integral de la VGI, no como complemento opcional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"203","text":"Corrección auditiva = prevención de deterioro cognitivo y caídas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"203","text":"Rehabilitación vestibular = prevención de caídas y pérdida de independencia","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"211","parent":"210","text":"Hipoacusia es el MAYOR factor de riesgo modificable para demencia (Lancet 2020)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"210","text":"Tapón de cerumen → descartar SIEMPRE, intervención más costo-efectiva en ORL geriátrica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"210","text":"Oye pero no entiende → problema de procesamiento central, no solo periférico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"210","text":"Implante coclear NO tiene límite de edad → evaluar candidatura en toda hipoacusia severa-profunda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"210","text":"HINTS > RMN en primeras 48h para diferenciar ACV de neuritis vestibular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"210","text":"Nistagmo vertical puro = CENTRAL hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"210","text":"Test impulso cefálico NORMAL en vértigo agudo = RED FLAG (pensar ACV cerebeloso)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"210","text":"Sedantes vestibulares crónicos → CONTRAINDICADOS, interfieren con compensación central","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"210","text":"VPPB → tratar con maniobras de reposición, NO con fármacos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"210","text":"MPPP → diagnóstico frecuente en AM con vértigo crónico, responde a rehabilitación + ISRS","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"210","text":"VGI sin evaluación sensorial = VGI INCOMPLETA","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"222","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"1. Livingston G et al. Dementia prevention, intervention, and care: 2020 report of the Lancet Commission. Lancet. 2020;396(10248):413-446.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"2. MINSAL Chile. Guía Clínica AUGE: Hipoacusia bilateral en personas de 65 años y más que requieren uso de audífono. 2013.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"222","text":"3. Cuda D et al. Improving quality of life in the elderly: hearing loss treatment with cochlear implants. BMC Geriatr. 2024;24(1):16.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"222","text":"4. von Brevern M et al. Benign paroxysmal positional vertigo: Diagnostic criteria. J Vestib Res. 2015;25:105-117.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"222","text":"5. Lempert T et al. Vestibular migraine: Diagnostic criteria. J Vestib Res. 2012;22(4):167-172.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"222","text":"6. Lopez-Escamez JA et al. Diagnostic criteria for Meniere's disease. J Vestib Res. 2015;25(1):1-7.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"222","text":"7. Strupp M et al. Acute unilateral vestibulopathy/vestibular neuritis: Diagnostic criteria. J Vestib Res. 2022;32(6):389-406.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"222","text":"8. Kim HA et al. Hemodynamic orthostatic dizziness/vertigo: Diagnostic criteria. J Vestib Res. 2019;29:45-56.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"222","text":"9. Kattah JC et al. HINTS to diagnose stroke in the acute vestibular syndrome. Stroke. 2009;40(11):3504-3510.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"222","text":"10. Gawronska A et al. Mobile devices in diagnosis and rehabilitation of balance disorders. Clin Interv Aging. 2020;15:2397-2406.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":232,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"ORL","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología","filename":"ORL Geriatrica iPad","id":"map_1572","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"ORL Geriatrica iPad"}